ğŸ› ï¸ 5. Key Insights for Troubleshooting

kubectl not working? â†’ Check API Server
Pods not scheduled? â†’ Check Scheduler
Pods unhealthy? â†’ Check Kubelet / CRI
Cluster state mismatch? â†’ Check Controller Manager
Networking issues? â†’ Check Kube-Proxy

Cloud integration failing? â†’ Check Cloud Controller Manager

